1. using str_split() function reverse string:

$str = str_split("Entrata");
$rev = "";
for ($i = count($str) - 1; $i >= 0; $i--) {
    $rev .= $str[$i];
}

echo $rev;



2. without using any predefine function() reverse string:
$no = 0;
while(isset($str[$no])) {
    $no++;
}

$str = "Entrata";
$rev = "";
for ($i = $no - 1; $i >= 0; $i--) {
    $rev .= $str[$i];
}

echo $rev;
